The Alex Jones Show

Monday January 05, 2009.

Alex welcomes back to the show Russell Blaylock, M.D., a retired neurosurgeon, and author of Excitotoxins: The Taste That Kills and The Blaylock Wellness Report.  Dr. Blaylock has demonstrated the link between food additives and degenerative diseases.  Alex also discusses the issues of the day and takes your calls.
